, I have two choices.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My Heart\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1217}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\" singer\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"a comeback\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"two choices\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Either I train like an athlete and work super hard, or I switch off and it's over, I stay at home, listen to my songs, stand in front of my mirror and sing to myself.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"my songs\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"my mirror\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have chosen to work with all my body and soul, from head to toe, with a medical team.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all my body\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"soul\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"toe\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"a medical team\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to be the best I can be.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My goal is to see the Eiffel Tower again!\\\"\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My goal\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last month, Dion released her documentary,I Am: Celine Dion, which provides an honest behind-the-scenes look at her life with SPS.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1784, \"end\": 1787, \"title\"